headline: Better Dividend Stock: Kinder Morgan vs. Enterprise Products Partners
summary: Kinder Morgan is one of the largest midstream operators in North America.  Enterprise Products Partners is one of the largest midstream operators in North America.  One of these two midstream giants has a better track record of reliably paying investors for sticking around.

headline: UBS Affirms ‘Buy’ Rating on Kinder Morgan (KMI) amid Arizona Expansion Plans
summary: Kinder Morgan, Inc. (NYSE:KMI) is one of Goldman Sachs’ top energy stock picks. On June 16, UBS reiterated a ‘Buy’ rating and a $38 price target on the stock.
